{
  "stem": "4289.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They came to a big-- like a room where there were clothes sitting in the, in the closets and told me, [NON-ENGLISH], do you want this?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], do you want that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I did, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't care that my father leaves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't want him to be with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I found out there are other children like myself, I got very friendly with them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they showed me how to play piano because I played a little piano.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they started to teach me how to pray in Hebrew and how to kiss the mezuzah when you come into the house, and all that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time I get by.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father said that the few weeks when he came to visit me, I was a changed child.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was happy there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the word Jew didn't bother me anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When I found out the other children are Jewish, too, I thought to myself, they're no different than the other one.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the people here were so nice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was never hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was clean.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My choices were like their wish to do anything for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They like me very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were very nice to each of the children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe at that time, my father registered me there as Ida Paluch.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the orphanage, my father came and picked me up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think he didn't settle all the business in Breslau, because he was supposed to get married to another lady who was also a survivor of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He put me in the house of his sister-in-law.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His brother did not survive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the sister-in-law survived, Frania.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I stayed with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She already was married to another man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were so nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
